Title: Beautopia
Writer: Mark Banker (story), Patrick McHale (story), Adam Muto, Kent Osborne (story), Rebecca Sugar, Pendleton Ward (story)
Actors: Jeremy Shada, John DiMaggio, Jackie Buscarino, Dee Bradley Baker
Plot: Susan Strong returns and asks Finn and Jake to save her people from the Glubs. But Finn is still not sure if he can trust her after last time.
